---
// Visual: Tool Landscape comparison
---
<div class="space-y-6">
  <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-text-muted">Three Tools, Three Philosophies</p>

  <div class="space-y-4">
    <!-- Claude Code -->
    <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-tool-claude/30 bg-tool-claude/5">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
        <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-tool-claude"></span>
        <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-tool-claude">Claude Code</span>
      </div>
      <p class="text-xs text-text-muted leading-relaxed">CLI-first. Anthropic models. Deep agentic loop. Runs in terminal, IDE, desktop, browser.</p>
      <div class="flex gap-1.5 mt-3 flex-wrap">
        <span class="text-[10px] px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-tool-claude/10 text-tool-claude rounded">Terminal</span>
        <span class="text-[10px] px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-tool-claude/10 text-tool-claude rounded">VS Code</span>
        <span class="text-[10px] px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-tool-claude/10 text-tool-claude rounded">Desktop</span>
        <span class="text-[10px] px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-tool-claude/10 text-tool-claude rounded">Web</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- OpenCode -->
    <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-tool-opencode/30 bg-tool-opencode/5">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
        <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-tool-opencode"></span>
        <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-tool-opencode">OpenCode</span>
      </div>
      <p class="text-xs text-text-muted leading-relaxed">Open source. Any LLM provider. Beautiful TUI. Full customization control.</p>
      <div class="flex gap-1.5 mt-3 flex-wrap">
        <span class="text-[10px] px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-tool-opencode/10 text-tool-opencode rounded">TUI</span>
        <span class="text-[10px] px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-tool-opencode/10 text-tool-opencode rounded">CLI</span>
        <span class="text-[10px] px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-tool-opencode/10 text-tool-opencode rounded">Web</span>
        <span class="text-[10px] px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-tool-opencode/10 text-tool-opencode rounded">IDE</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Copilot -->
    <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-tool-copilot/30 bg-tool-copilot/5">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
        <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-tool-copilot"></span>
        <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-tool-copilot">GitHub Copilot</span>
      </div>
      <p class="text-xs text-text-muted leading-relaxed">IDE-native. GitHub integrated. Multi-model. Inline completions + chat + agent.</p>
      <div class="flex gap-1.5 mt-3 flex-wrap">
        <span class="text-[10px] px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-tool-copilot/10 text-tool-copilot rounded">VS Code</span>
        <span class="text-[10px] px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-tool-copilot/10 text-tool-copilot rounded">JetBrains</span>
        <span class="text-[10px] px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-tool-copilot/10 text-tool-copilot rounded">CLI</span>
        <span class="text-[10px] px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-tool-copilot/10 text-tool-copilot rounded">Web</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Shared DNA -->
  <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-border bg-surface/50 mt-6">
    <p class="text-xs text-text-muted uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Shared DNA</p>
    <div class="space-y-1.5 text-xs text-text-secondary">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-accent">+</span> MCP support</div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-accent">+</span> Agentic capabilities</div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-accent">+</span> Custom instructions</div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-accent">+</span> Code review</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
